                    </div>
                    <span>This book changed my life by helping me to no longer live dishonestly with myself. By taking a minute here and there for my "self," I met my "self" and learned just exactly what I want to do and how I want  to live. I find freedom in every decision now, by letting go of those  things I do not truly care for, and focussing only on the good. Now I am  able to find the good in everything. More importantly I know a most  important truth: I am who I am.</span>
                  
              
